	Success requirements
*	*	*	*	*	*	*	*	*
-database for live events: stores socket.io room id; stores initial scoreboard data;
-website for live events: shows current live events, reading from database; if no live events, link to past events site;
-past events site lists all past events;
-event template: called with post method, receives data of the event
-administration site
	-login secured
	-add/remove live events
	-remote control
		-manipulate current live event

